{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:1","prev_osis_id":"Isa.065.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le vrai culte<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. (Ac 17:24, 25. \u00c9s 57:15.) \u00c9s 65:3-15. Lu 21:17-24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Le ciel est mon tr\u00f4ne,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la terre mon marchepied.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quelle maison pourriez-vous me b\u00e2tir,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et quel lieu me donneriez-vous pour demeure?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.65.25","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 65:25","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.65.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:2","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Toutes ces choses, ma main les a faites,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et toutes ont re\u00e7u l\u2019existence, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici sur qui je porterai mes regards:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sur celui qui souffre et qui a l\u2019esprit abattu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sur celui qui craint ma parole.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:3","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Celui qui immole un b\u0153uf est comme celui qui tuerait un homme,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celui qui sacrifie un agneau est comme celui qui romprait la nuque \u00e0 un chien,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celui qui pr\u00e9sente une offrande est comme celui qui r\u00e9pandrait du sang de porc,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celui qui br\u00fble de l\u2019encens est comme celui qui adorerait des idoles;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tous ceux-l\u00e0 se complaisent dans leurs voies,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et leur \u00e2me trouve du plaisir dans leurs abominations.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:4","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Moi aussi, je me complairai dans leur infortune,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je ferai venir sur eux ce qui cause leur effroi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Parce que j\u2019ai appel\u00e9, et qu\u2019ils n\u2019ont point r\u00e9pondu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Parce que j\u2019ai parl\u00e9, et qu\u2019ils n\u2019ont point \u00e9cout\u00e9;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Mais ils ont fait ce qui est mal \u00e0 mes yeux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils ont choisi ce qui me d\u00e9pla\u00eet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:5","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\u00c9coutez la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Vous qui craignez sa parole.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici ce que disent vos fr\u00e8res,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui vous ha\u00efssent et vous repoussent<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A cause de mon nom:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Que l\u2019\u00c9ternel montre sa gloire,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que nous voyions votre joie!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais ils seront confondus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:6","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Une voix \u00e9clatante sort de la ville,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Une voix sort du temple.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est la voix de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui paie \u00e0 ses ennemis leur salaire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:7","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Gloire de la nouvelle J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-14: cf. Ro 11:12, 15, 23-26. (\u00c9s 60:11-18; 65:17-25.) H\u00e9 12:22-24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Avant d\u2019\u00e9prouver les douleurs,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle a enfant\u00e9;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Avant que les souffrances lui vinssent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle a donn\u00e9 naissance \u00e0 un fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:8","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Qui a jamais entendu pareille chose<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui a jamais vu rien de semblable?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Un pays peut-il na\u00eetre en un jour?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Une nation est-elle enfant\u00e9e d\u2019un seul coup?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A peine en travail, Sion a enfant\u00e9 ses fils!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:9","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Ouvrirais-je le sein maternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour ne pas laisser enfanter? Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Moi, qui fais na\u00eetre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Emp\u00eacherais-je d\u2019enfanter? Dit ton Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:10","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>R\u00e9jouissez-vous avec J\u00e9rusalem,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Faites d\u2019elle le sujet de votre all\u00e9gresse,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Vous tous qui l\u2019aimez;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tressaillez avec elle de joie,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Vous tous qui menez deuil sur elle;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:11","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Afin que vous soyez nourris et rassasi\u00e9s<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Du lait de ses consolations,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Afin que vous savouriez avec bonheur<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La pl\u00e9nitude de sa gloire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:12","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>\n    Car ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici, je dirigerai vers elle la paix comme un fleuve,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la gloire des nations comme un torrent d\u00e9bord\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et vous serez allait\u00e9s;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Vous serez port\u00e9s sur les bras,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et caress\u00e9s sur les genoux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:13","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Comme un homme que sa m\u00e8re console,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ainsi je vous consolerai;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Vous serez consol\u00e9s dans J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:14","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Vous le verrez, et votre c\u0153ur sera dans la joie,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et vos os reprendront de la vigueur comme l\u2019herbe;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019\u00c9ternel manifestera sa puissance envers ses serviteurs,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais il fera sentir sa col\u00e8re \u00e0 ses ennemis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.15","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.15","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:15","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Jugement des m\u00e9chants<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-24: cf. Ap 19:11-21. (\u00c9s 11:10; 60:3-12.) H\u00e9 12:27-29.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Car voici, l\u2019\u00c9ternel arrive dans un feu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ses chars sont comme un tourbillon;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il convertit sa col\u00e8re en un brasier,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ses menaces en flammes de feu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.16","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.16","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:16","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>C\u2019est par le feu que l\u2019\u00c9ternel exerce ses jugements,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est par son glaive qu\u2019il ch\u00e2tie toute chair;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ceux que tuera l\u2019\u00c9ternel seront en grand nombre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.15","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.17","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:17","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ceux qui se sanctifient et se purifient dans les jardins,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Au milieu desquels ils vont un \u00e0 un,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui mangent de la chair de porc,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Des choses abominables et des souris,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tous ceux-l\u00e0 p\u00e9riront, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.18","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:18","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.16","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.18","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:18","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Je connais leurs \u0153uvres et leurs pens\u00e9es.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le temps est venu de rassembler toutes les nations<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et toutes les langues;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles viendront et verront ma gloire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.19","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:19","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.19","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:19","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Je mettrai un signe parmi elles,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et j\u2019enverrai leurs r\u00e9chapp\u00e9s vers les nations,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A Tarsis, \u00e0 Pul et \u00e0 Lud, qui tirent de l\u2019arc,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A Tubal et \u00e0 Javan,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Aux \u00eeles lointaines,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui jamais n\u2019ont entendu parler de moi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et qui n\u2019ont pas vu ma gloire;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils publieront ma gloire parmi les nations.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.20","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:20","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.18","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:18","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.20","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:20","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Ils am\u00e8neront tous vos fr\u00e8res du milieu de toutes les nations,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">En offrande \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sur des chevaux, des chars et des liti\u00e8res,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sur des mulets et des dromadaires,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A ma montagne sainte,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A J\u00e9rusalem, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl apportent leur offrande,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dans un vase pur,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.21","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:21","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.19","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:19","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.21","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:21","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et je prendrai aussi parmi eux<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Des sacrificateurs, des L\u00e9vites, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.22","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:22","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.20","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:20","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.22","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:22","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Car, comme les nouveaux cieux<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la nouvelle terre que je vais cr\u00e9er<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Subsisteront devant moi, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ainsi subsisteront votre post\u00e9rit\u00e9 et votre nom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.23","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:23","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.21","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:21","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.23","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:23","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.066.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>A chaque nouvelle lune et \u00e0 chaque sabbat,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Toute chair viendra se prosterner devant moi, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.24","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:24","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.22","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:22","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.24","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:24","prev_osis_id":"Isa.066.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.66.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Et quand on sortira, on verra<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Les cadavres des hommes qui se sont rebell\u00e9s contre moi;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Car leur ver ne mourra point, et leur feu ne s\u2019\u00e9teindra point;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils seront pour toute chair un objet d\u2019horreur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.66","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.1.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.66.23","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 66:23","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.66.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb65e2b80.32050159');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb65e2b80.32050159\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb65e2b80.32050159","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb65e